0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T01:54:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岩岩學 目標係4年考8級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好太執著考級</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAgger <br />\n利申 考左8級但係覺得自己對鋼琴都係零</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76af5e5952c78b593841378dba2cf907bcb095ad","tid":902,"uid":3904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:18:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>古典撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n超級中意去聽音樂會<br />\n嚟緊考CU MUSIC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n祝你做到我師弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真問 面試筆試有咩要注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCU相對BU 同APA 無咁睇重演奏水平<br />\n相反會睇你個人對音樂嘅理念<br />\n我當年考入去得張DipABRSM<br />\n但就吹到自己想改變香港音樂教育嘅扭曲現象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你入到複試會有written 同aural <br />\nWritten 大約係8級theory 難度再加啲general knowledge <br />\nGeneral knowledge 真係乜都有，連中樂同jazz都有，睇你見識有幾廣<br />\nAural 就sight singing 同melody dictation <br />\n我記得好似係8個bar<br />\n<br />\n不過我係3年大學年代，果時個系主任都係2012年過左身<br />\n而家個新系主任要求嘅嘢未必一樣"},{"pid":"95a980e4afa2d7e8a1eaa11711545b2bbd15a430","tid":902,"uid":13908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:20:33.000Z","msg":"弦樂撚<br />\n<br />\n學左廿年 classical 都黎緊<br 